{
 "name": "RPlog_Meaning_of_the_Dark_Side",
 "title": "The Meaning of the Dark Side",
 "summary": "The Jedi woman Ai'kani confronts the Sith apprentice Dareus on a quiet world, but instead of striking him down she engages him in a circling, philosophical duel of words about weeds, viruses, peace and passion. Rather than fighting, she lays a hand on his head and draws him into a shared Force vision, a storm of blinding light, fire, screaming darkness, and the visions of his Master that test and measure his soul. Through this intimate, disorienting communion, punctuated by a ground-shaking kiss, she shows him the true nature of both sides of the Force. Dareus emerges shaken and newly aware of a weakness he had never perceived in himself, his certainty about his chosen path quietly unsettled.",
